text: Nature Law or Break () is a 2014 Chinese-Singaporean romantic comedy film directed by Li Jian and Qiu Zhongwei. It was released on November 7. ==Cast== *Eva Huang *Jia Yiping *Johnny Zhang *Liu Tianzuo *Lam Suet *Xiao Jian *Jiang Hongbo *Liu Huan *Yue Yueli *Li Jing ==Reception== By November 7, the film had earned ¥1.03 million at the Chinese box office. ==References== Category:2014 romantic comedy films Category:Chinese romantic comedy films Category:Chinese films Category:Singaporean films Category:Singaporean romantic comedy films Category:2014 comedy films
